Subject: [PATCH] I-wire-003 B4 (#1317): fix quantified_analysis silent no-op +
 harden canary
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit

Root cause (file:line): the prod _q_spec_provider closure in
scripts/run_honest_sweep_r3.py:10448 called the GLM-5.2 generator with a
starved max_tokens=4000. z-ai/glm-5.2 is an _ALWAYS_REASON model
(openrouter_client.py:812) -> _call() floors it only to PG_GLM5_MIN_MAX_TOKENS=4096
(openrouter_client.py:1778-1796), far below the ~17K-char reasoning prelude
GLM-5.2 emits before content (openrouter_client.py:3368-3372). The whole budget
is consumed by reasoning, content comes back empty, the reasoning stream itself
truncates before the JSON spec closes, the {.*} recovery finds no complete
object -> SpecProviderTransportError -> spec_provider_error -> spec_produced=False
-> fired=False (the phase-7 canary the I-wire-002 replay preflight tripped; the
drb72/drb90 fixtures show the same shape: 111/91 sourced numbers in,
spec_produced=False out).

Fix (§9.1.8 never-starve): raise the closure budget to a generous env-tunable
PG_QUANTIFIED_SPEC_MAX_TOKENS (default 32768) so the reasoning-first generator
finishes BOTH its prelude AND emits the closing-brace JSON spec. Also SPLIT the
closure's old "non-dict OR model_id falsy" decline branch so a truncated-but-
parseable spec MISSING model_id is raised as a parse fault, not masqueraded as a
benign decline.

Canary hardening: _quantified_readiness_failed now consumes the typed
quantified_status/firing_status to distinguish ran-and-legitimately-empty
(declined_no_spec / no_verified_sentences -> disclose, do NOT abort) from
silently-broke/skipped (parse_error / empty_transport / spec_provider_error /
spec_validation_rejected / execution_failed / telemetry=None -> FAIL LOUD).
Unclassifiable shapes fall back to the #1237 fired-only fail so no silent green.

Faithfulness NOT relaxed: a ModelSpec is small DATA validated by
build_quantified_spec; the budget is billed by actual usage. No strict_verify /
NLI / 4-role D8 / provenance gate touched; the canary only ever DEMOTES a
would-be success.

Tests: tests/polaris_graph/synthesis/test_quantified_b4_fire_iwire003.py (fire on
a representative basket; canary trips on a forced transport no-op; explicit
decline stays honest-empty) + 5 new readiness-split cases in
tests/polaris_graph/blockers/test_g2_runsweep_blockers.py. 44 passed.

